  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Agent Observability\nThe chat agent end to end: turn volume and token spend, how the router classifies each turn (tier + intent), conversation latency and errors, MCP tool usage, and voice time-to-first-audio. Sections below: **Overview** (turns & tokens) \u00b7 **Routing & intent** (how turns are classified) \u00b7 **Conversation** (throughput, latency, errors) \u00b7 **Tools** (MCP call volume, latency, errors) \u00b7 **Voice** (time to first audio). Hover any panel's title (\u24d8) for details and threshold meanings. Alarm thresholds are starting proposals, retunable."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 200,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Overview",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total turns (24h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(increase(agent_turns_total[24h]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "color": {
            "mode": "fixed",
            "fixedColor": "blue"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "Total chat turns in the last 24h \u2014 every user message that reached the agent and produced a response. The headline volume number the rest of the dashboard breaks down."
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tokens in (24h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
